- **tailwind-variants** -- used by component internals for variant styling (includes tailwind-merge under the hood)
- **tw-animate-css** -- replaces the deprecated `tailwindcss-animate`; provides animation utilities for Tailwind v4
- **@lucide/svelte** -- icon library used by shadcn-svelte components

**bits-ui** is only needed when you add components that depend on it (e.g., dialog, popover, dropdown-menu). You can install it later as needed: `pnpm i bits-ui`

### 2. components.json

Your existing file at `/Users/alr/git/ALRubinger/aileron/ui/components.json` is already close. The correct format is:

```json
{
  "$schema": "https://shadcn-svelte.com/schema.json",
  "tailwind": {
    "css": "src/app.css",
    "baseColor": "neutral"
  },
  "aliases": {
    "components": "$lib/components",
    "utils": "$lib/utils",
    "ui": "$lib/components/ui",
    "hooks": "$lib/hooks",
    "lib": "$lib"
  },
  "typescript": true,
  "registry": "https://shadcn-svelte.com/registry"
}
```

This file is only needed if you use the CLI to add components (`pnpm dlx shadcn-svelte@latest add button`), but it is good to have for documentation purposes.

